column1: The #COVID19 pandemic has hit our small businesses hard and we need to get out to support them. Don’t forget to #ShopLocal today for Small Business Saturday.

The Communist Chinese regime destroyed valuable data silenced doctors and blocked an investigation into the origin of #COVID19. They are responsible for this pandemic and we must continue to hold them accountable. https://t.co/lbRNMCSoUi

Communist China hid and destroyed evidence regarding #COVID19. We must continue to hold them accountable. That’s exactly what President @realDonaldTrump and Vice Pres. @Mike_Pence are doing. #KAG2020 #VPDebate #MAGA

President @realDonaldTrump & Vice President @Mike_Pence did the right thing by banning travel from China early on. The Trump Administration has taken decisive action towards defeating the invisible enemy #COVID19. #MAGA #VPDebate

It's time to put America back in 'DRIVE'. We know now that our COVID response should focus on the most vulnerable. We can and should move forward with both common sense AND our personal liberties. #TN6
Thank you to all of the nurses and other health care professionals who have been working non-stop to help those suffering from #COVID19. We appreciate all you do.

Just six weeks ago President @realDonaldTrump was in TN to provide support after the devastating tornadoes. Now he continues to lead the fight to slow the spread of #COVID19 & get America back to work. I support him and am Grateful he is OUR President.
